quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  43,61,"It is the knowledge of the Hour. Have no doubt concerning it, and follow me. This is a Straight Path,"
  43,62,"and do let satan prevent you, for he is your clear enemy."
  43,63,"And when (Prophet) Jesus came with clear signs, he said: 'I have come to you with wisdom and to clarify to you some of the matters about which you differ. Fear Allah and obey me."
  43,64,"Indeed, Allah is my Lord and your Lord, therefore worship Him. That is the Straight Path'"
  43,65,"Yet the parties differed among themselves. So woe to those who did evil among the punishment of a Painful Day."
  43,66,"Are they looking for anything except the Hour (to overtake them). It will come upon them suddenly when they are unaware!"
  43,67,"On that Day close friends shall become enemies of each other, except those who fear (Allah)."
  43,68,"O My worshipers, there is no fear for you on this Day, nor will you grieve"
  43,69,"to those who believed in Our verses and were Muslims,"
  43,70,"(it will be said) 'You and your spouses, enter, walking with joy into Paradise'"
  43,71,"To them will be passed large platters and cups of gold. There will be all that souls desire and all that eyes delight in. (And it will be said:) 'There you shall live for ever."
  43,72,"Such is the Paradise you shall inherit, for the things you did."
  43,73,"You shall have therein abundant fruit to eat'"